#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "&sheets; Basics"
msgstr "&sheets; Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the rest of &kde;, &sheets; is highly configurable, which can cause "
"problems for readers trying to compare the text in a document such as this "
"with what they see on the version of &sheets; running on their desktop. To "
"cut down on some of the possibilities for confusion, it is suggested that "
"when you first start to use &sheets; you set the default options in all "
"pages of the &sheets; configuration dialog (obtained by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Sheets...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot ostalo v &kde;, je &sheets; zelo prilagodljiv, kar lahko povzroči "
"težave bralcem, ki poskušajo primerjati besedilo v dokumentu, kot je ta, s "
"tem, kar vidijo v različici &sheets; tečejo na njihovem namizju. Da bi "
"zmanjšali nekatere možnosti za zmedo, predlagamo, da ko prvič začnete "
"uporabljati &sheets; nastavite privzete možnosti na vseh straneh &sheets; "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno (dobite ga tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj liste...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheets for Beginners"
msgstr "Preglednice za začetnike"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section attempts to explain by example what a spreadsheet program such "
"as &sheets; actually does, and why it is such a useful tool in any situation "
"where you have to deal with numbers. If you have already used a spreadsheet "
"program you may wish to skip to the next section."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek poskuša na primeru razložiti, kaj je program preglednice, kot je "
"&sheets; kaj dejansko počne in zakaj je tako uporabno orodje v vsaki "
"situaciji, ko se morate ukvarjati s številkami. Če ste že uporabljali "
"program za preglednice, boste morda želeli preskočiti na naslednji razdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first thing to do is to start up &sheets;. You can do this by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on a &sheets; icon if there is one "
"on your desktop or panel, or you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Office</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar je, da zaženete &sheets;. To lahko storite tako, da "
"<mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> kliknete na ikono &sheets;, če je na vašem "
"namizju ali plošči, lahko pa izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Office</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v zaganjalniku "
"aplikacij."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "&sheets; at first run"
msgstr "&sheets; ob prvem teku"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it has started you will be given the choice of opening a recent "
"document, creating a new document from a template (with templates "
"categories) or opening an existing document . Select the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> category on the left and choose the <guilabel>Blank Worksheet</"
"guilabel> template. Then click the <guibutton>Use This Template</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Ko se zažene, boste imeli na izbiro odpiranje nedavnega dokumenta, "
"ustvarjanje novega dokumenta iz predloge (s kategorijami predlog) ali "
"odpiranje obstoječega dokumenta. Izberite kategorijo <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel> na levi in izberite predlogo <guilabel>Prazen delovni list</"
"guilabel>. Nato kliknite gumb <guibutton>Uporabi to predlogo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Looking at &sheets; once it has started up, you will see a sheet of empty "
"rectangular cells arranged in numbered rows and lettered columns. This is "
"where you enter data or formula, text or charts."
msgstr ""
"Če pogledamo &sheets; ko se zažene, boste videli list praznih pravokotnih "
"celic, razporejenih v oštevilčene vrstice in stolpce s črkami. Tukaj vnesete "
"podatke ali formulo, besedilo ali grafikone."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot starting1"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona se začne 1"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, enter the text and values shown in the first 5 rows of the above "
"screenshot into the same cells of your spreadsheet. Ignore what is in row 7 "
"for the moment. To enter anything into a cell first select the cell by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking inside it, then type whatever you "
"want, then press &Enter; or use the arrow keys to move the selection point "
"to another cell."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj vnesite besedilo in vrednosti, prikazane v prvih 5 vrsticah zgornjega "
"posnetka zaslona, v iste celice vaše preglednice. Zaenkrat prezrite, kar je "
"v 7. vrstici. Če želite kar koli vnesti v celico, najprej izberite celico z "
"<mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> klikom znotraj nje, nato vnesite, kar "
"želite, nato pritisnite &Enter; ali uporabite puščične tipke, da premaknete "
"izbirno točko v drugo celico."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What we have entered so far could be a simple budget for the next two "
"months, listing how much we think we will be spending for Food, Shelter, "
"Clothing and any Other expenditure. Now select cell B7 (column B, row 7), "
"type in <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> and press &Enter;. Because it "
"begins with a <keycap>=</keycap> symbol &sheets; sees this as a formula, "
"something it has to calculate, in this case by adding together the values in "
"the 4 cells B2 to B5, and what is shown in the cell B7 is the result of that "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"Kar smo do zdaj vnesli, bi lahko bil preprost proračun za naslednja dva "
"meseca, ki navaja, koliko mislimo, da bomo porabili za hrano, stanovanje, "
"oblačila in vse druge izdatke. Zdaj izberite celico B7 (stolpec B, vrstica "
"7), vnesite <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> in pritisnite &Enter;. Ker "
"se začne s simbolom <keycap>=</keycap> &sheets; vidi to kot formulo, nekaj, "
"kar mora izračunati, v tem primeru tako, da sešteje vrednosti v 4 celicah B2 "
"do B5, in kar je prikazano v celici B7, je rezultat tega izračuna."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could enter a similar formula into cell C7, except that in this case it "
"would have to be <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, but there is an easier "
"way which is to Copy cell B7 and Paste it into C7. &sheets; will "
"automatically adjust the cell references from B.. to C.. when the Paste is "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Podobno formulo bi lahko vnesli v celico C7, le da bi v tem primeru morala "
"biti <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, vendar obstaja lažji način, in "
"sicer Kopiranje celice B7 in Prilepi v C7. &sheets; bo samodejno prilagodil "
"sklice na celice iz B.. v C.., ko je lepljenje končano."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At this point you may think that &sheets; is doing no more than you could "
"manage with pencil, paper and a calculator, and you could be right, but "
"remember that this is a very small example of a spreadsheet, doing simple "
"calculations on only a few numbers. For any reasonably amount of values or "
"data using a spreadsheet to do the calculations is much quicker and more "
"accurate than doing them manually."
msgstr ""
"Na tej točki lahko mislite, da &sheets; ne naredi več, kot bi vam uspelo s "
"svinčnikom, papirjem in kalkulatorjem, in morda imate prav, vendar ne "
"pozabite, da je to zelo majhen primer preglednice, ki izvaja preproste "
"izračune le z nekaj številkami. Za razumno količino vrednosti ali podatkov "
"je uporaba preglednice za izračune veliko hitrejša in natančnejša kot ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, a spreadsheet lets you play the <quote>What if?</quote> game. Because "
"each formula is automatically recalculated whenever any of the values it "
"refers to are changed, you can quickly see what happens if you alter any of "
"them. Using our example you can see the effect of reducing the amount spent "
"on food in December by just entering a new value into cell C2. If you had a "
"spreadsheet that modelled the greenhouse effect accurately you could perhaps "
"see the effect of a 50 percent reduction in the amount of methane released "
"into the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega vam preglednica omogoča igranje igre <quote>Kaj če?</quote>. Ker "
"se vsaka formula samodejno znova izračuna vsakič, ko se spremeni katera koli "
"vrednost, na katero se nanaša, lahko hitro vidite, kaj se zgodi, če katero "
"koli od njih spremenite. Na našem primeru lahko vidite učinek zmanjšanja "
"zneska, porabljenega za hrano v decembru, tako da preprosto vnesete novo "
"vrednost v celico C2. Če bi imeli preglednico, ki natančno modelira učinek "
"tople grede, bi morda lahko videli učinek 50-odstotnega zmanjšanja količine "
"metana, sproščenega v ozračje."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Cells"
msgstr "Izbiranje celic"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select a single cell or a rectangular area of cells in the "
"spreadsheet. The selected cell(s) are displayed with a thick black border."
msgstr ""
"V preglednici lahko izberete eno celico ali pravokotno območje celic. "
"Izbrane celice so prikazane z debelim črnim robom."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select a single cell in one of the following ways"
msgstr "Posamezno celico lahko izberete na enega od naslednjih načinov"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on it"
msgstr "<mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> klik nanj"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"enter the cell reference (for example <userinput>B5</userinput>) into the "
"cell reference box at the left end of the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> "
"tool options and press &Enter;"
msgstr ""
"vnesite sklic na celico (na primer <userinput>B5</userinput>) v polje za "
"sklic na celico na levem koncu možnosti orodja <guilabel>Urejevalnik celic</"
"guilabel> in pritisnite &Enter;"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option"
msgstr ""
"uporabite menijsko možnost <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pojdi na celico...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also steer your way around with the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. "
"Pressing the &Enter; key will move the current selection one position up, "
"down, left or right depending on the setting in the <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel> page of &sheets;'s <link linkend=\"configinterface\">configuration "
"dialog box</link>."
msgstr ""
"Svojo pot lahko premikate tudi s <keysym>puščicami</keysym>. S pritiskom "
"tipke &Enter; tipka premakne trenutni izbor za en položaj navzgor, navzdol, "
"levo ali desno, odvisno od nastavitve na strani <guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel> "
"<link linkend=\"configinterface\">konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna</link> "
"&sheets; ."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> key down while "
"using the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys the selection will move to the start "
"or end of the block of occupied cells."
msgstr ""
"Če držite tipko <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> med uporabo "
"<keysym>puščičnih tipk</keysym>, se izbor premakne na začetek ali konec "
"bloka zasedenih celic."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select an area of contiguous cells drag the mouse cursor across the "
"desired area with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down, or "
"enter the references of the top left and bottom right cells separated by a "
"colon into the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> cell reference box (for "
"example <userinput>B7:C14</userinput>) and press &Enter;, or enter these "
"cell references in a similar format into the dialog box brought up by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati območje sosednjih celic, povlecite kazalec miške čez "
"želeno območje z <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> gumbom, ki ga držite "
"pritisnjenim, ali vnesite sklice na zgornje leve in spodnje desne celice, "
"ločene z dvopičjem, v <guilabel> Urejevalnik celice </guilabel> referenčno "
"polje celice (na primer <userinput>B7:C14</userinput>) in pritisnite &Enter; "
"ali vnesite te reference celic v podobni obliki v pogovorno okno, ki ga "
"odpre <menuchoice><guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pojdi na celico...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select an area of cells by selecting the cell in one corner of "
"the wanted area then holding the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; </"
"keycombo> key down while using the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse "
"button to select the cell in the opposite corner."
msgstr ""
"Območje celic lahko izberete tudi tako, da izberete celico v enem kotu "
"želenega območja in pridržite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; </keycombo> "
"tipko navzdol, medtem ko z <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> tipko miške "
"izberete celico v nasprotnem kotu."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous cells, click on the first cell you want to select "
"then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and select "
"the other cells."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati nesosednje celice, kliknite prvo celico, ki jo želite "
"izbrati, nato držite tipko <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> in "
"izberite druge celice."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a complete row or column of cells <mousebutton>left </mousebutton> "
"click on the row number at the left of the worksheet or on the column "
"letters at the top. To select adjacent rows or columns drag the mouse "
"pointer over the appropriate row numbers or column letters with the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati celotno vrstico ali stolpec celic <mousebutton>levo </"
"mousebutton> kliknite na številko vrstice na levi strani delovnega lista ali "
"na črke stolpca na vrhu. Če želite izbrati sosednje vrstice ali stolpce, "
"povlecite miškin kazalec čez ustrezne številke vrstic ali črke stolpcev in "
"pridržite <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous rows or columns of cells, click on the first row "
"number or column letter then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</"
"keycombo> key and select the other rows or columns of cells."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati nesosednje vrstice ali stolpce celic, kliknite številko "
"prve vrstice ali črko stolpca, nato držite tipko <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> in izberite druge vrstice ali stolpce celic."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Data"
msgstr "Vnos podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering data into a cell can be as simple as selecting the cell, typing "
"your data, then pressing &Enter; or moving the selection to another cell "
"with one of the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. Depending on how you enter the "
"data, &sheets; will interpret it as a number, date, time or text:"
msgstr ""
"Vnos podatkov v celico je lahko tako preprost, kot da izberete celico, "
"vnesete podatke in nato pritisnete &Enter; ali premaknite izbor v drugo "
"celico z eno od <keysym>puščičnih</keysym> tipk. Odvisno od tega, kako "
"vnesete podatke, &sheets; ga bo interpretiral kot številko, datum, čas ali "
"besedilo:"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Numbers are entered in the obvious way; <userinput>123</userinput>, "
"<userinput> -123</userinput>, <userinput>456.7</userinput> or in scientific "
"notation <userinput>-1.2E-5</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Številke se vnašajo na očiten način; <userinput>123</userinput>, <userinput> "
"-123</userinput>, <userinput>456.7</userinput> ali v znanstveni notaciji "
"<userinput>-1.2E-5</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dates should be entered in your <quote>System</quote> format, as defined in "
"the &systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu> "
"Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> tab. If, for example, you are using the DD/MM/"
"YYYY form you should enter <userinput>30/03/2012</userinput> for 30th March "
"2012. Leading zeroes can be omitted from the day and month fields and only "
"the last one or two digits of the year need to be entered if the date is in "
"the current century, for example <userinput>9/1/9</userinput> for 9th "
"January 2009."
msgstr ""
"Datumi morajo biti vneseni v vašem <quote>sistemskem</quote> formatu, kot je "
"določeno v &systemsettings; v <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu> Država/regija &amp; Jezik</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; "
"Čas</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> zavihek. Če na primer uporabljate obrazec DD/"
"MM/LLLL, morate vnesti <userinput>30/03/2012</userinput> za 30. marec 2012. "
"Začetne ničle lahko izpustite iz polj za dan in mesec in samo zadnje vnesti "
"je treba eno ali dve števki leta, če je datum v tekočem stoletju, na primer "
"<userinput>9/1/9</userinput> za 9. januar 2009."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Times should also be entered using the <quote>System</quote> format. For "
"example if you are using a 12 hour clock then enter times in HH:MIN am|pm or "
"HH:MIN:SS am|pm format such as <userinput>9:42 am</userinput> or <userinput> "
"10:30:52 pm</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Čase je treba vnesti tudi v obliki zapisa <quote>Sistem</quote>. Na primer, "
"če uporabljate 12-urno uro, vnesite čase v formatu HH:MIN am|pm ali HH:MIN:"
"SS am|pm, na primer <userinput>9:42</userinput> ali <userinput> 10:30 :52</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; defines any input data as <quote>text</quote> if it cannot "
"recognize the data as being a number, date or time."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; definira vse vhodne podatke kot <quote>besedilo</quote>, če ne more "
"prepoznati podatkov kot števila, datuma ali ure."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &sheets; right justifies numbers, dates and times within a cell "
"and left justifies anything else. This can be a useful guide to whether you "
"have entered a date or time in the correct format. But remember that how "
"items are displayed can be changed by altering the <link linkend=\"formatdata"
"\">cell format</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &sheets; desno poravna številke, datume in čase v celici, levo pa "
"karkoli drugega. To je lahko koristen vodnik, ali ste vnesli datum ali čas v "
"pravilni obliki. Ne pozabite pa, da lahko način prikaza elementov spremenite "
"tako, da spremenite <link linkend=\"formatdata\">format celice</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main text entry box in the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> tool options "
"provides an easy way of editing the contents of a selected cell. Press "
"&Enter; or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the green tick mark when "
"you are happy with what you have entered, or click on the red cross to "
"cancel your edits."
msgstr ""
"Glavno polje za vnos besedila v možnostih orodja <guilabel>Urejevalnik "
"celic</guilabel> omogoča preprost način urejanja vsebine izbrane celice. "
"Pritisnite &Enter; ali <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> kliknite na zeleno "
"kljukico, ko ste zadovoljni z vnesenim, ali kliknite na rdeči križ, da "
"prekličete urejanje."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Cell Format"
msgstr "Generični format celice"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; uses the <quote>Generic</quote> cell format as default. As long as "
"this format is used, &sheets; autodetects the actual data type depending on "
"the current cell data. For example if you enter some text into a cell and "
"later enter a number into the same cell, &sheets; automatically interprets "
"the new data as a number. If you want to define the type of data yourself, "
"you can explicitly set it in the <link linkend=\"formatdata\">cell format</"
"link>. You can change the format back to <quote>Generic</quote> at any time."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; kot privzeto uporablja <quote>Generičen</quote> format celice. "
"Dokler se ta oblika uporablja, &sheets; samodejno zazna dejanski tip "
"podatkov glede na trenutne podatke celice. Če na primer v celico vnesete "
"nekaj besedila in pozneje v isto celico vnesete številko, &sheets; samodejno "
"interpretira nove podatke kot število. Če želite vrsto podatkov določiti "
"sami, jo lahko izrecno nastavite v <link linkend=\"formatdata\">formatu "
"celice</link>. Format lahko kadar koli spremenite nazaj v <quote>Generic</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy, Cut and Paste"
msgstr "Kopiraj, izreži in prilepi"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At first glance, &sheets;'s <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> appear "
"to be similar to these functions in other &kde; applications. Having "
"selected a cell or cells, you can choose <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu or from "
"the drop down menu you get by holding the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button down on a selected cell. You can also use the shortcuts "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo>, then move the "
"selection to the target cell and choose <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. "
"However there are some subtleties associated with these functions in "
"&sheets; and these are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"Na prvi pogled se zdi, da so <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> "
"&sheets; podobne tem funkcijam v drugih &kde; aplikacije. Ko izberete celico "
"ali celice, lahko izberete <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> ali v "
"spustnem meniju, ki ga dobite, če držite <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> "
"gumb miške navzdol na izbrano celico. Uporabite lahko tudi bližnjice "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> ali "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo >, nato "
"premaknite izbor v ciljno celico in izberite <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem> ali pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Vendar pa je s temi funkcijami v &sheets; nekaj "
"posebnosti in ti so obravnavane spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a cell contains a formula then the formula itself is copied rather than "
"the displayed result, and if the formula contains a reference to another "
"cell, then that reference is changed by the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> "
"operation to point to the cell that is in the same relative position as in "
"the original cell. For example if cell A2 contains the formula <userinput> "
"=B3</userinput> and is copied to C4, cell C4 will contain <userinput>=D5 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če celica vsebuje formulo, se sama formula kopira namesto prikazanega "
"rezultata, in če formula vsebuje sklic na drugo celico, se ta sklic spremeni "
"z <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> "
"in <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> operacijo, ki kaže na celico, ki je v "
"istem relativnem položaju kot v prvotni celici. Če celica A2 na primer "
"vsebuje formulo <userinput> =B3</userinput> in je kopirana v C4, bo celica "
"C4 vsebovala <userinput>=D5 </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may seem to be a rather strange way of doing a copy, but 99 percent of "
"the time it is exactly what is wanted (if it is not then see the section "
"about <link linkend=\"absolute\">absolute cell references</link>). For "
"example in the simple shopping list shown below, cell D2 should contain "
"<userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 should be <userinput>=B3 * C3</"
"userinput>, D4 should be <userinput>=B4 * C4</userinput> and so on. Instead "
"of having to enter a different formula in each cell, you can just enter the "
"first formula into D2 and then copy it into the cells below, letting "
"&sheets; adjust the cell references to suit."
msgstr ""
"To se morda zdi precej nenavaden način kopiranja, vendar je v 99 odstotkih "
"primerov točno tisto, kar želimo (če ni, si oglejte razdelek o <link linkend="
"\"absolute\">absolutnih sklicih na celice</link >). Na preprostem "
"nakupovalnem seznamu, prikazanem spodaj, mora na primer celica D2 vsebovati "
"<userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 mora biti <userinput>=B3 * C3</"
"userinput>, D4 mora biti <userinput>=B4 * C4</userinput> in tako naprej. "
"Namesto da bi morali vnesti drugo formulo v vsako celico, lahko preprosto "
"vnesete prvo formulo v D2 in jo nato kopirate v spodnje celice, tako da "
"&sheets; prilagodite sklice na celice, da ustrezajo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot copy1"
msgstr "Kopija posnetka zaslona1"

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying and Pasting Cell Areas"
msgstr "Kopiranje in lepljenje območij celic"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the above example D2 can be copied into all three cells D3 to D5 at once "
"by just copying D2 then selecting the complete cell area D3:D5 before doing "
"the paste."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem primeru je mogoče D2 kopirati v vse tri celice D3 do D5 naenkrat "
"tako, da preprosto kopirate D2 in nato izberete celotno območje celice D3:"
"D5, preden izvedete lepljenje."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A rectangular area of cells can be cut or copied in one operation by "
"selecting the area before doing the cut or copy. Then select the top left "
"corner cell of the area you want to paste into before doing the paste."
msgstr ""
"Pravokotno območje celic je mogoče izrezati ali kopirati v eni operaciji, "
"tako da izberete območje, preden naredite izrez ali kopiranje. Nato izberite "
"celico v zgornjem levem kotu območja, kamor želite prilepiti, preden začnete "
"lepiti."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cut or copy a rectangular area of cells, say B2:C3, and paste it into "
"a larger area such as A10:D13 the original pattern of cells will be repeated "
"to fill the target area."
msgstr ""
"Če izrežete ali kopirate pravokotno območje celic, recimo B2:C3, in ga "
"prilepite v večje območje, kot je A10:D13, se bo prvotni vzorec celic "
"ponovil, da bo zapolnil ciljno območje."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also provides a <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method for copying "
"cells down into other cells immediately below or to the right of the "
"original cell(s). To use this method select the cell(s) to be copied then "
"position the mouse pointer over the small black square at the bottom right "
"corner of the selected cell(s) so the cursor changes to a double headed "
"arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while "
"you drag the selected cell(s) as far as you wish. Note that cell references "
"in formulae are incremented according to the relative position change. "
"Absolute references are not changed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; nudi tudi metodo <quote>povleci in kopiraj</quote> za kopiranje "
"celic navzdol v druge celice neposredno pod ali desno od prvotne celice(e). "
"Če želite uporabiti to metodo, izberite celico(e), ki jo želite kopirati, "
"nato postavite kazalec miške na majhen črni kvadratek v spodnjem desnem kotu "
"izbrane celice(e), da se kazalec spremeni v dvosmerno puščico. Nato držite "
"pritisnjen <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> gumb miške, medtem ko vlečete "
"izbrane celice, kolikor želite. Upoštevajte, da se sklice na celice v "
"formulah povečajo glede na spremembo relativnega položaja. Absolutne "
"reference se ne spreminjajo."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Paste Modes"
msgstr "Drugi načini lepljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A cell may contain text, a value, or a formula, and may also contain special "
"font, border or background <link linkend=\"formatspread\">formatting "
"information</link>. &sheets; has special versions of Paste that let you "
"handle these items in different ways."
msgstr ""
"Celica lahko vsebuje besedilo, vrednost ali formulo in lahko vsebuje tudi "
"<link linkend=\"formatspread\">podatke o oblikovanju</link> posebne pisave, "
"obrobe ali ozadja. &sheets; ima posebne različice lepljenja, ki vam "
"omogočajo, da s temi predmeti ravnate na različne načine."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>brings up the <guilabel> Special Paste</guilabel> "
"dialog box. By selecting the appropriate item from the left part of this "
"dialog you can choose to paste <guilabel>Everything</guilabel>, just "
"<guilabel>Text</guilabel>, the cell <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, any "
"<guilabel>Comment</guilabel> in the cell(s) or <guilabel>Everything without "
"border</guilabel>. The items in the right part of this dialog box allow you "
"to do simple <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">arithmetic on an area of "
"cells</link>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Posebno lepljenje...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>prikliče pogovorno okno <guilabel>Posebno "
"lepljenje</guilabel>. Z izbiro ustreznega elementa v levem delu tega "
"pogovornega okna lahko izberete, da prilepite <guilabel>Vse</guilabel>, samo "
"<guilabel>Besedilo</guilabel>, celico <guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>, kateri "
"koli <guilabel >Komentar</guilabel> v celici(-ah) ali <guilabel>Vse brez "
"obrobe</guilabel>. Elementi v desnem delu tega pogovornega okna vam "
"omogočajo preprosto <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">aritmetiko na območju "
"celic</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Paste with Insertion...</guimenuitem> inserts the copied "
"cell(s) into the sheet by moving the cells that would otherwise be "
"overwritten a suitable number of rows of columns down or to the right. It "
"can also be used to insert complete copied row(s) or column(s) into the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi z vstavljanjem...</guimenuitem> vstavi kopirano(-e) "
"celico(-e) na list tako, da premakne celice, ki bi bile sicer prepisane, za "
"ustrezno število vrstic stolpcev navzdol ali v desno. Uporablja se lahko "
"tudi za vstavljanje celotnih kopiranih vrstic ali stolpcev v delovni list."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert and Delete"
msgstr "Vstavi in izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <keysym>Del</keysym> key or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Contents</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> to remove the text, value or formula from selected cell(s), "
"row(s) or column(s) without affecting anything else."
msgstr ""
"S tipko <keysym>Del</keysym> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Počisti</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vsebina</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> odstranite besedilo, vrednost oz. formulo iz izbranih celic, "
"vrstic ali stolpcev, ne da bi to vplivalo na karkoli drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete everything in the selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s), including "
"comments and special formatting, choose the <guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem> "
"option from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu or from the pop up menu you get when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a selection."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati vse v izbranih celicah, vrsticah ali stolpcih, vključno "
"s komentarji in posebnim oblikovanjem, v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> izberite možnost <guimenuitem>Vse</guimenuitem> "
"><guisubmenu>Počisti</guisubmenu></menuchoice> meni ali iz pojavnega menija, "
"ki se prikaže, ko <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete izbor."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove selected row(s) or column(s) completely, use the "
"<guimenuitem>Delete Rows</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Delete Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v celoti odstraniti izbrane vrstice ali stolpce, uporabite "
"možnosti <guimenuitem>Izbriši vrstice</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Izbriši "
"stolpce</guimenuitem> v pojavnem oknu z <mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> "
"gumbom miške meni."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a cell or cells and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Cells... </"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button pop up "
"menu, you can then choose whether other cells in the worksheet will be moved "
"up or to the left to fill in the space left by the cell(s) you have chosen "
"to remove."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete celico ali celice in izberete <guimenuitem>Odstrani celice ... </"
"guimenuitem> v pojavnem meniju <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke miške, "
"lahko nato izberete, ali bodo druge celice na delovnem listu premaknjene "
"navzgor ali v levo, da zapolnite prostor, ki ga puščajo celice, ki ste jih "
"izbrali za odstranitev."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert new, blank, row(s) or column(s) into the sheet, select "
"row(s) or column(s) where you wish the new row(s) or column(s) to be placed "
"and choose the <guimenuitem>Insert Rows</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Insert "
"Columns</guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton> right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v list vstaviti nove, prazne vrstice ali stolpce, izberite vrstice "
"ali stolpce, kamor želite postaviti nove vrstice ali stolpce, in izberite "
"možnost <guimenuitem>Vstavi vrstice</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Vstavi "
"stolpce</guimenuitem> v pojavnem meniju z <mousebutton> desnim</mousebutton> "
"gumbom miške."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert new cells into the worksheet by selecting the area where you "
"want them to appear then choosing the <guimenuitem> Insert Cells...</"
"guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu. You will then be asked whether the existing cell(s) in the "
"selected area should be moved down or to the right to make room for the new "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"Nove celice lahko vstavite v delovni list tako, da izberete območje, kjer "
"želite, da se prikažejo, nato pa izberete možnost <guimenuitem> Vstavi "
"celice...</guimenuitem> v pojavnem meniju <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> "
"tipke miške. Nato boste pozvani, ali naj obstoječe celice v izbranem območju "
"premaknete navzdol ali v desno, da naredite prostor za nove."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Sums"
msgstr "Enostavne vsote"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the first character in a cell is an equals sign (<keycap>=</keycap>) "
"&sheets; will take the cell contents to be a formula which is to be "
"calculated. The result of the calculation will be displayed in the cell "
"rather than the formula itself. For example, enter <userinput>=2+3</"
"userinput> into a cell and it should display <emphasis>5</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Če je prvi znak v celici znak enačaja (<keycap>=</keycap>) bo &sheets; vzel "
"vsebino celice za formulo, ki jo je treba izračunati. Rezultat izračuna bo "
"prikazan v celici namesto same formule. Vnesite na primer <userinput>=2+3</"
"userinput> v celico in prikazano bi moralo biti <emphasis>5</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More usefully, a formula can contain references to other cells, so that "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> will calculate the sum of the values in cells "
"B4 and A3, and this calculation will be updated whenever cells B4 or A3 are "
"changed."
msgstr ""
"Bolj uporabno je, da lahko formula vsebuje sklice na druge celice, tako da "
"bo <userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> izračunal vsoto vrednosti v celicah B4 in "
"A3, ta izračun pa bo posodobljen vsakič, ko sta celici B4 ali A3 spremenjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as addition, a formula can make use of the <keycap>-</keycap> symbol "
"for subtraction, <keycap>*</keycap> for multiplication, and <keycap> /</"
"keycap> to perform division. The round bracket symbols <keycap>(</keycap> "
"and <keycap>)</keycap> can also be used as in normal algebra, so you could "
"enter more complex formulae such as <userinput>=((B10 + C3) *5 - F11) / 2 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Poleg seštevanja lahko formula uporablja simbol <keycap>-</keycap> za "
"odštevanje, <keycap>*</keycap> za množenje in <keycap> /</keycap> za "
"izvajanje deljenja. Simbole z okroglim oklepajem <keycap>(</keycap> in "
"<keycap>)</keycap> lahko uporabite tudi kot v običajni algebri, tako da "
"lahko vnesete bolj zapletene formule, kot je <userinput>=((B10 + C3) * 5 - "
"F11) / 2 </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cells containing a formula will be marked with a small blue triangle at the "
"bottom left corner if the <guilabel>Show formula indicator</guilabel> check "
"box in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sheet Properties</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> dialog is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Celice, ki vsebujejo formulo, bodo označene z majhnim modrim trikotnikom v "
"spodnjem levem kotu, če potrdite polje <guilabel>Pokaži indikator formule</"
"guilabel> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Lastnosti lista</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> pogovorno "
"okno je označeno."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also includes a large number of built-in functions for applications "
"such as statistical, trigonometrical and financial calculations. Their use "
"will be examined in more depth in a <link linkend=\"formulas\"> later "
"section</link> of this manual, but if you are interested at this stage "
"choose <guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Insert</"
"guimenu> menu and take a look through the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> "
"dialog box that will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; vključuje tudi veliko število vgrajenih funkcij za aplikacije, kot "
"so statistični, trigonometrični in finančni izračuni. Njihova uporaba bo "
"podrobneje preučena v <link linkend=\"formulas\"> kasnejšem razdelku</link> "
"tega priročnika, če pa vas na tej stopnji zanima, izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Funkcija...</guimenuitem> iz Meni <guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu> in "
"si oglejte pogovorno okno <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel>, ki se bo prikazalo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the time being, however, the <userinput>SUM</userinput> function may be "
"of interest as it calculates the sum of all values in a specified area of "
"cells. For example <userinput>=SUM(B4:C10)</userinput> calculates the sum of "
"all values in the cell area B4 to C10."
msgstr ""
"Zaenkrat pa je lahko zanimiva funkcija <userinput>SUM</userinput>, saj "
"izračuna vsoto vseh vrednosti v določenem območju celic. Na primer "
"<userinput>=SUM(B4:C10)</userinput> izračuna vsoto vseh vrednosti v območju "
"celic B4 do C10."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &sheets; displays <keycap>#VALUE!</keycap> when you have entered your "
"formula this usually means that it cannot understand what you have entered, "
"but if the row of symbols ends with a small red arrow this just means that "
"the cell is not wide enough to display the complete result, in which case "
"you should either make the cell(s) wider or change their <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">format</link> so that the result does fit properly."
msgstr ""
"Če &sheets; prikaže <keycap>#VALUE!</keycap>, ko vnesete svojo formulo, to "
"običajno pomeni, da ne more razumeti, kaj ste vnesli, če pa se vrstica "
"simbolov konča z majhno rdečo puščico, to samo pomeni, da celica ni dovolj "
"široka za prikaz celotnega rezultata; v tem primeru razširite celico(e) ali "
"spremenite njihovo <link linkend=\"formatdata\">obliko</link>, da se "
"rezultat pravilno prilega."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recalculation"
msgstr "Preračun"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Automatic recalculation</guilabel> box in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sheet Properties</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> dialog "
"box is checked, &sheets; will recalculate the values of cells whenever "
"anything that affects them is changed in the sheet."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno polje <guilabel>Samodejni ponovni izračun</guilabel> v "
"pogovornem oknu <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Lastnosti lista</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, bo "
"&sheets; znova izračunal vrednosti celic, kadar koli se na listu spremeni "
"kar koli, kar vpliva nanje."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Automatic recalculation</guilabel> is not checked for the "
"current sheet, you can instruct &sheets; to perform a recalculation at any "
"time by using the <guimenuitem>Recalculate Sheet</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem> Recalculate Document</guimenuitem> option in the "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu or their shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keysym>F9</keysym> </keycombo> or <keysym>F9</keysym>."
msgstr ""
"Ko <guilabel>Samodejni ponovni izračun</guilabel> ni označen za trenutni "
"list, lahko naročite &sheets; da izvedete ponoven izračun kadar koli z "
"uporabo možnosti <guimenuitem>Ponovni izračun lista</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem> Ponovni izračun dokumenta</guimenuitem> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> ali njunih bližnjic <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keysym>F9</keysym> </keycombo> ali <keysym>F9</keysym>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting Data"
msgstr "Razvrščanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the simple example shown below, the data consist of the names and "
"countries of a number of mountains together with their height above sea "
"level. &sheets; can sort data such as this in different ways."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem preprostem primeru so podatki sestavljeni iz imen in držav "
"številnih gora skupaj z njihovo višino nad morsko gladino. &sheets; lahko "
"razvrsti podatke, kot so ti, na različne načine."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of sorted data"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona razvrščenih podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We may want the data sorted so that the names are in alphabetical order. To "
"do this select the area containing the data (A2:C7 in this case) and choose "
"<guimenuitem>Sort...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. "
"This opens the <guilabel>Sort</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Morda želimo, da so podatki razvrščeni tako, da so imena po abecednem "
"vrstnem redu. Če želite to narediti, izberite območje, ki vsebuje podatke (v "
"tem primeru A2:C7) in izberite <guimenuitem>Razvrsti...</guimenuitem> v "
"meniju <guimenu>Podatki</guimenu>. To odpre pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Razvrsti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sorting is done alphanumerically, and the default is case sensitive, numbers "
"coming before uppercase letters which come before lowercase letters, so that "
"cells containing the entries <userinput>Cat</userinput>, <userinput>bar</"
"userinput>, <userinput>77</userinput> and <userinput>Bat</userinput> would "
"be sorted into the following order: <emphasis>77 Bat Cat bar</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Razvrščanje poteka alfanumerično in privzeto je občutljivo na velike črke, "
"številke so pred velikimi črkami, ki so pred malimi črkami, tako da celice, "
"ki vsebujejo vnose <userinput>Cat</userinput>, <userinput>bar</userinput>, "
"<userinput> 77</userinput> in <userinput>Bat</userinput> bi bila razvrščena "
"v naslednjem vrstnem redu: <emphasis>77 Bat Cat bar</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Direction</guilabel> area of this dialog box select to sort "
"in rows or columns. If you check the <guilabel>First row contains column "
"headers</guilabel> or <guilabel>First column contains row headers</guilabel> "
"box data in the first row or column will not be included in the sort "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"V območju <guilabel>Smer</guilabel> tega pogovornega okna izberite "
"razvrščanje po vrsticah ali stolpcih. Če označite polje <guilabel>Prva "
"vrstica vsebuje glave stolpcev</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Prvi stolpec vsebuje "
"glave vrstic</guilabel>, podatki v prvi vrstici ali stolpcu ne bodo "
"vključeni v operacijo razvrščanja."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rows or columns are sorted in the specified order, which can be changed "
"using the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and <guibutton>Move Down</"
"guibutton> buttons. Using the example in the above screenshot, choosing "
"column B as the first key and column C as the second would sort the data by "
"country and, for each country, by height."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice ali stolpci so razvrščeni v določenem vrstnem redu, ki ga lahko "
"spremenite z gumboma <guibutton>Premakni gor</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Premakni dol</guibutton>. Z uporabo primera na zgornjem posnetku "
"zaslona bi izbira stolpca B kot prvega ključa in stolpca C kot drugega "
"razvrstila podatke po državi in za vsako državo po višini."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck the option <guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel> to get a sort not "
"depending on capitalization and switch the sort order between "
"<guilabel>Ascending</guilabel> and <guilabel>Descending</guilabel> by "
"clicking on the cells in the column <guilabel>Sort Order</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Počistite možnost <guilabel>Razlikuje med malimi in malimi črkami</"
"guilabel>, da dobite razvrščanje, ki ni odvisno od velikih začetnic, in "
"preklopite vrstni red razvrščanja med <guilabel>Naraščajoče</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Padajoče</guilabel> s klikom na celice v stolpec <guilabel>Vrstni "
"red</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Details >></guilabel> extension of the dialog allows you to "
"sort using the order of items in a custom list such as January, February... "
"instead of alphanumerically. The cell format is moved with the cell content, "
"if you select <guilabel>Copy cell formatting (Borders, Colors, Text Style)</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Razširitev pogovornega okna <guilabel>Podrobnosti >></guilabel> vam omogoča "
"razvrščanje po vrstnem redu elementov na seznamu po meri, kot je januar, "
"februar... namesto alfanumerično. Oblika celice se premakne z vsebino "
"celice, če izberete <guilabel>Kopiraj oblikovanje celice (obrobe, barve, "
"slog besedila)</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Status bar Summary Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator povzetka vrstice stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left hand end of the Status bar by default shows a summary of the values "
"in the selected cell(s). According to the setting of the <guilabel>Function "
"shown in status bar</guilabel> combo box in the <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel> page of &sheets;'s configuration dialog the summary can be:"
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani vrstice stanja je privzeto prikazan povzetek vrednosti v "
"izbranih celicah. Glede na nastavitev kombiniranega polja "
"<guilabel>Funkcija, prikazana v vrstici stanja</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel> konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna &sheets; je "
"lahko povzetek:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Noben"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "No summary calculation is performed."
msgstr "Izračun povzetka se ne izvede."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Average"
msgstr "Povprečje"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the average of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je povprečje vrednosti v izbranih celicah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Count"
msgstr "Štetje"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the number of cells containing numeric values."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je število celic, ki vsebujejo številske vrednosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "CountA"
msgstr "CountA"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the number of non empty cells."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je število celic, ki niso prazne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Max</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Max</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the maximum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je največja vrednost v izbranih celicah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Min</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Min</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the minimum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je najmanjša od vrednosti v izbranih celicah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Sum</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Sum</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the sum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana vrednost je vsota vrednosti v izbranih celicah."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The method of calculation can also be changed by <mousebutton>right </"
"mousebutton> clicking on the summary calculation result area of the Status "
"bar and choosing an item from the pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Način izračuna lahko spremenite tudi tako, da z <mousebutton>desno </"
"mousebutton> kliknete območje rezultatov povzetka izračuna v vrstici stanja "
"in izberete element v pojavnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving your Work"
msgstr "Shranjevanje vašega dela"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; saves the complete document, which may include more than one "
"worksheet, as a single document file."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; shrani celoten dokument, ki lahko vključuje več kot en delovni "
"list, kot eno datoteko dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have created a new document, or want to save an existing one under a "
"different name, use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem> Save "
"As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will bring up &kde;'s common "
"<guilabel>Save Document As</guilabel> dialog box. Choose the folder where "
"you want to save the document and enter a suitable file name into the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel> text box. &sheets; documents are normally "
"automatically saved with a <filename>.ods</filename> extension, you do not "
"need to add this to the filename but do make sure that the <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel> selection is set to <guilabel>OpenDocument SpreadSheet</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če ste ustvarili nov dokument ali želite obstoječega shraniti pod drugim "
"imenom, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Shrani kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To bo prikazalo običajno pogovorno "
"okno &kde; <guilabel>Shrani dokument kot</guilabel>. Izberite mapo, v katero "
"želite shraniti dokument, in v besedilno polje <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> "
"vnesite ustrezno ime datoteke. &sheets; dokumenti se običajno samodejno "
"shranijo s pripono <filename>.ods</filename>, tega vam ni treba dodati imenu "
"datoteke, vendar se prepričajte, da je izbira <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> "
"nastavljena na <guilabel>OpenDocument Preglednica</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To save your document without changing its name, just use <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite shraniti dokument, ne da bi spremenili njegovo ime, uporabite "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also save a &sheets; document in a foreign format selecting the "
"format from the <guilabel>Filter:</guilabel> combo box."
msgstr ""
"Shranite lahko tudi &sheets; dokument v tuji obliki z izbiro oblike v "
"kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Filter:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you save a modified version of an existing document &sheets; will keep "
"the previous version as a backup file, adding a <literal>~</literal> to the "
"end of the filename."
msgstr ""
"Ko shranite spremenjeno različico obstoječega dokumenta &sheets; bo ohranil "
"prejšnjo različico kot datoteko varnostne kopije in dodal <literal>~</"
"literal> na konec imena datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can provide some protection against losing your work because of a "
"computer crash or because you have closed &sheets; without saving the "
"current document. It does this by automatically saving the latest version of "
"the document you are working on every few minutes using a modified file "
"name. The autosaved version is normally removed when you next save your "
"document, so that it will only exist if it is more up to date than the "
"version that was saved manually. When you open a document &sheets; checks to "
"see if an autosaved version exists, and if it finds one it will offer to "
"open that instead."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; lahko zagotovi nekaj zaščite pred izgubo vašega dela zaradi sesutja "
"računalnika ali ker ste zaprli &sheets; brez shranjevanja trenutnega "
"dokumenta. To naredi tako, da samodejno shrani najnovejšo različico "
"dokumenta, na katerem delate, vsakih nekaj minut s spremenjenim imenom "
"datoteke. Samodejno shranjena različica se običajno odstrani, ko naslednjič "
"shranite dokument, tako da bo obstajal samo, če je novejši od različice, ki "
"ste jo shranili ročno. Ko odprete dokument &sheets; preveri, ali obstaja "
"samodejno shranjena različica, in če jo najde, namesto tega ponudi, da jo "
"odpre."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Autosaved documents are saved with a file name of the form <filename>."
"yourfilename.autosave</filename> (note the leading period), so that "
"<filename>spread1.ods</filename> would be autosaved as <filename>.spread1."
"ods.autosave</filename>. The autosave feature is user configurable in the "
"<link linkend=\"configopensave\">settings dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno shranjeni dokumenti so shranjeni z imenom datoteke v obliki "
"<filename>.yourfilename.autosave</filename> (upoštevajte uvodno piko), tako "
"da bi bil <filename>spread1.ods</filename> samodejno shranjen kot <filename>."
"spread1 .ods.autosave</filename>. Funkcijo samodejnega shranjevanja lahko "
"uporabnik konfigurira v <link linkend=\"configopensave\">pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates"
msgstr "Predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are going to be creating a lot of similar documents you can save "
"yourself time and trouble by first creating a template and then using that "
"as the basis for the individual documents."
msgstr ""
"Če boste ustvarili veliko podobnih dokumentov, si lahko prihranite čas in "
"težave tako, da najprej ustvarite predlogo in jo nato uporabite kot osnovo "
"za posamezne dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do this first create a document containing the common elements, then save "
"it as a template by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Create Template From Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Doing "
"this opens the <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box. Enter a name "
"for your new template into the <guilabel>Name:</guilabel> text box and press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The next time you start a new document by "
"choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or when you next start &sheets; the startup dialog window will "
"give you the option of creating the new document from your template."
msgstr ""
"Če želite to narediti, najprej ustvarite dokument, ki vsebuje običajne "
"elemente, nato pa ga shranite kot predlogo z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustvari predlogo iz "
"dokumenta</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. S tem se odpre pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Ustvari predlogo</guilabel>. V besedilno polje <guilabel>Ime:</"
"guilabel> vnesite ime svoje nove predloge in pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>. Ko naslednjič zaženete nov dokument z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali ko naslednjič zaženete &sheets; zagonsko pogovorno okno vam "
"bo ponudilo možnost ustvarjanja novega dokumenta iz vaše predloge."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box also lets you choose a "
"different picture to be displayed above the template name in the startup "
"dialog window, and lets you save your templates under different group names, "
"which will appear as different pages in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Ustvari predlogo</guilabel> vam prav tako omogoča, "
"da izberete drugo sliko, ki bo prikazana nad imenom predloge v pogovornem "
"oknu ob zagonu, in vam omogoča, da shranite svoje predloge pod različnimi "
"imeni skupin, ki bodo prikazane kot različne strani v dialog."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Templates are stored as <literal role=\"extension\">.kst</literal> files "
"under <filename>~/.kde/share/apps/tables/templates/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Predloge so shranjene kot datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">.kst</"
"literal> pod <filename>~/.kde/share/apps/tables/templates/</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing a Spreadsheet"
msgstr "Tiskanje preglednice"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Printing a spreadsheet is basically done by selecting <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"which brings up &kde;'s common <guilabel>Print</guilabel> dialog box where "
"you can choose, among other options, the printer to be used, the number of "
"copies and whether all or only selected pages are to be printed."
msgstr ""
"Tiskanje preglednice poteka v bistvu tako, da izberete <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, kar prikliče običajni <guilabel>Natisni</guilabel> &kde; "
"pogovorno okno, kjer lahko med drugimi možnostmi izberete tiskalnik, ki ga "
"želite uporabiti, število kopij in ali naj se natisnejo vse ali samo izbrane "
"strani."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &sheets; will print all items in the current worksheet, but you "
"can restrict this by first selecting the area that you want to be printed "
"then choosing <guimenuitem>Define Print Range</guimenuitem> from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Print Range</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &sheets; bo natisnil vse elemente na trenutnem delovnem listu, "
"vendar lahko to omejite tako, da najprej izberete območje, ki ga želite "
"natisniti, nato pa izberete <guimenuitem>Določi obseg tiskanja</guimenuitem> "
"v <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> Podmeni <guisubmenu>Obseg tiskanja</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; will print as many pages as are necessary to include all items in "
"the current worksheet. You can quickly see how a worksheet will be split "
"into separate pages for printing by checking the <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Page Borders</guimenuitem></menuchoice> box. The "
"boundaries of each printed page will then be marked by colored lines in the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; bo natisnil toliko strani, kot je potrebnih za vključitev vseh "
"elementov v trenutnem delovnem listu. Hitro si lahko ogledate, kako bo "
"delovni list razdeljen na ločene strani za tiskanje, tako da potrdite polje "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obrobe strani</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Meje vsake natisnjene strani bodo nato označene z "
"barvnimi črtami na delovnem listu."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a more detailed view of what is to be sent to the printer, including "
"anything you have asked to be included in the page headers and footers (see "
"below), choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print "
"Preview...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnejši pregled tega, kar je treba poslati v tiskalnik, vključno z "
"vsem, kar ste zahtevali, da se vključi v glave in noge strani (glejte "
"spodaj), izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni Predogled...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To improve the appearance of the printed output , you can change the fonts, "
"colors, borders and sizes of the cells in the worksheet, see the <link "
"linkend=\"formatspread\">Spreadsheet Formatting</link> section for more "
"details about how to do this."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izboljšati videz natisnjenega izpisa, lahko spremenite pisave, "
"barve, obrobe in velikosti celic na delovnem listu; glejte razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"formatspread\">Oblikovanje preglednice</link> za več podrobnosti o "
"tem, kako to storite."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guilabel>Page Layout</guilabel> dialog box, invoked by "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Page Layout...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, to change the orientation of the printed pages, "
"the paper size (this should be suitable for your printer) and the size of "
"the page borders."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi pogovorno okno <guilabel>Postavitev strani</guilabel>, "
"ki ga prikličete tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Postavitev strani...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da "
"spremenite orientacijo natisnjenih strani, velikost papirja (ta mora "
"ustrezati vašemu tiskalniku) in velikost robov strani."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sheet</guilabel> provides more options. The <guilabel>Print "
"settings</guilabel> section lets you select whether or not to print the "
"grid, comment indicators and formula indicators, objects and charts. The "
"<guilabel>Repetitions on each page</guilabel> section allows you to repeat "
"selected column(s) or row(s) on each printed page. In the section "
"<guilabel>Scaling</guilabel> you can set a scalefactor or the page limits "
"for the print."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>List</guilabel> ponuja več možnosti. Razdelek <guilabel>Nastavitve "
"tiskanja</guilabel> vam omogoča, da izberete, ali želite natisniti mrežo, "
"indikatorje komentarjev in indikatorje formul, predmete in grafikone. "
"Razdelek <guilabel>Ponovitve na vsaki strani</guilabel> vam omogoča "
"ponavljanje izbranih stolpcev ali vrstic na vsaki natisnjeni strani. V "
"razdelku <guilabel>Prilagajanje velikosti</guilabel> lahko nastavite faktor "
"merila ali omejitve strani za tiskanje."
